Broken Bridge
Create a function which validates whether a bridge is safe to walk on (i.e. has no gaps in it to fall through).

Examples
isSafeBridge("####") ➞ true

isSafeBridge("## ####") ➞ false

isSafeBridge("#") ➞ true
Notes
You can expect the bridge's ends connecting it to its surrounding.

My Solution

function isSafeBridge(str) {
	let dude = str.split(" ")
	if (dude.length === 1){
		return true
	} else return false
}
